      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The bedrock of a strong nation is the traditional family, a unit built on commitment, faith, and shared values. We must stand firm against the corrosive tide of modern progressive ideologies that seek to dismantle what has made our society great. Our candidate champions the foundational principles that have sustained generations, defending the sanctity of life and the enduring strength of the American home. It is time to reclaim our values and build a future rooted in tradition, not radical upheaval.",
